{
  "texts": [
    "Li et al. 's [8] \"DeepPatent\" with convolutional neural networks and word embeddings contributes to evolving and refining CPC's capabilities.",
    "Furthermore, studies enhanced CPC using BERT techniques, elevating patent document classification accuracy and efficiency.",
    "Lee and Hsiang fine-tuned a BERT model for patent classification in their pioneering work \"PatentBERT\" [9].In the latest research conducted in 2023, the exploration of the Cooperative Patent Classification (CPC) system has continued to evolve.",
    "Yoo et al. [11] examine multi-label classification of Artificial Intelligence-related patents, utilizing Modified D2SBERT and Sentence Attention mechanisms.",
    "Meanwhile, Ha and Lee [12] explores the effectiveness of the CPC system, focusing on patent embeddings."
  ]
}